## Overview

AuthDemo is a multi-project solution built on .NET 8, featuring a Blazor web application, secure API services, and integrated authentication/authorization using ASP.NET Core Identity and OpenIddict. The solution demonstrates modern identity management, role-based access, and secure communication between client and server.

